00:19:20.260 --> 00:19:22.730 position:24% line:83% align:start
-(dramatic booming)
-Behold, as I answer you.

00:19:22.764 --> 00:19:24.666 position:27% line:89% align:start
(intense booming)

00:19:24.699 --> 00:19:26.067 position:30% line:89% align:start
Satisfied yet?

00:19:26.100 --> 00:19:27.635 position:30% line:83% align:start
-There's more.
-Huh?

00:19:27.669 --> 00:19:30.270 position:35% line:83% align:start
You should
brace yourself first,

00:19:30.303 --> 00:19:33.074 position:24% line:83% align:start
and then, look down
when you're ready.

00:19:33.107 --> 00:19:34.274 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:19:35.143 --> 00:19:37.310 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Ikkyu]
(gasps)

00:19:37.779 --> 00:19:39.747 position:30% line:89% align:start
(shocked gasp)

00:19:39.781 --> 00:19:41.248 position:13% line:89% align:start
Who's the rule-breaker now?

00:19:41.281 --> 00:19:44.018 position:19% line:83% align:start
I mean, I'll admit this
isn't the plot I envisioned,

00:19:44.052 --> 00:19:45.252 position:44% line:83% align:start
but,
given the tight deadline,

00:19:45.285 --> 00:19:47.354 position:24% line:83% align:start
