Heaven's Door.

00:19:54.028 --> 00:19:55.228 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasp)

00:19:55.797 --> 00:19:57.264 position:24% line:89% align:start
(dramatic booming)

00:19:57.297 --> 00:19:59.232 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Rohan] Oh, look!
You're doing it again.

00:19:59.266 --> 00:20:02.670 position:24% line:83% align:start
-(nervous gasping)
