00:20:39.507 --> 00:20:42.442 position:16% line:83% align:start
My my, it seems the gods
have no quarrel with me.

00:20:42.476 --> 00:20:43.745 position:24% line:89% align:start
And why would they,

00:20:43.778 --> 00:20:46.313 position:13% line:83% align:start
